## Common Feature File Patterns

### Pattern 1: DataTable (for form data)
```gherkin
Scenario: User fills registration form
  When the user fills the registration form with:
    | Field     | Value              |
    | Full Name | Pavan Kumar        |
    | Email     | pavan@example.com  |
    | Phone     | 9876543210         |
  And the user submits the form
  Then the registration success message should appear
```

### Pattern 2: Scenario Outline (data-driven)
```gherkin
Scenario Outline: Search products by category
  When the user searches for "<category>"
  Then the results should show products under "<expected_section>"

  Examples:
    | category    | expected_section |
    | Electronics | Gadgets          |
    | Clothing    | Apparel          |
    | Books       | Literature       |
```

### Pattern 3: Background (common setup)
```gherkin
Background:
  Given the user is logged in as "admin"
  And the user navigates to the orders page
```

